[Effect] 
 precise query: the number/bar code must be exactly the same as the input content to be queried 
 fuzzy query: The number/bar code as long as the input content can be queried 
 left fuzzy query: The part after the number/bar code contains the input content can be queried 
 right fuzzy query: The part before the number/bar code contains the input content can be queried 

 
 [Suggestion] 
 fuzzy query, the more the input content the more accurate the query, it is recommended to input more content 

 
 [Note] 
1. Any kind of fuzzy query will reduce the query efficiency, especially in the case of large data volume may cause the query jam; Please turn on 
2 according to the actual need. After the fuzzy query is turned on, the functions "identify the goods and quantity according to the barcode rules", "remove the last digit of the barcode scanned by the invoice", and "enter at least the last digit of the barcode when retrieving the barcode" do not take effect.

Keyword fuzzy search: According to the search configuration items, the global fuzzy query is performed to list all the search results. Progressive search is not supported.
Keyword progressive search: For each search, the search is performed in the last query result to achieve a progressive search. Usage: After entering keywords each time, press the space bar to continue to enter keywords.
